<h3>Submit A Bug</h3>
<p>
Use this screen to submit a new bug to the official email address for bug reports, <a href="mailto:bugs@coldboxframework.com">bugs@coldboxframework.com</a>.

<ul>
	<li>This form uses the CF engine's mail settings to send the bug report. Please verify your coldfusion mail settings.</li>
	<li>Please not that the From Email Address field, will be used as the FROM in the cfmail tag.</li>
</ul>
</p>